     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <head>MOLA{W}D I‘R A{W}DVR.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>O G{y}mhenjaith deg a‘i m{y}nnu,</l>
      <l>{Y} mae t{y} nnu ammod doniog:</l>
      <l>A‘r hoph {w}enjaith, a bair ph{y}nnu,</l>
      <l>G{w}yr enn{y}nnu gair ja{w}n en{w}og.</l>
      <l>Nid oedh bhudion,</l>
      <l>Nag ehudion,</l>
      <l>Beirdh a Drudion braidh droeadog:</l>
      <l>Perri pur{w}aith</l>
      <l>Vn{w}edh jo{w}n{w}aith</l>
      <l>Euraid araith y{w} ‘r dioriog.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>O e{y} mer{w}n a‘i e{y}mharu,</l>
      <l>{W}iria caru eiriau caerog;</l>
      <l>Idho adbher{w}n dhi‘dibharu</l>
      <l>A darparu dra{w} hap eurog.</l>
      <l>Am buroriaith</l>
      <l>A blaeanoriaith</l>
      <l>A rhagoriaith orau geiriog.</l>
      <l>Mae‘n ph{y}nnad{w}y,</l>
      <l>Mae‘n barchad{w}y,</l>
      <l>Mae‘n dalad{w}y m{w}yn d{y}ledog.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>O gelbh{y}dhyd golau bhodhion,</l>
      <l>Da y{w} rhodhion da{w}n rhiedhog;</l>
      <l>{Y} no n{y} dhid a{w}en nodhion</l>
      <l>Ag ansodhion g{w}i{w} na{w}s hedhog.</l>
      <l>A chanmol{w}ch</l>
      <l>A rheol{w}ch</l>
      <l>
         <pb facs="8"/>
A dadol{w}ch di{w}yd el{w}og:</l>
      <l>{Y}n bhedrus-{w}ych</l>
      <l>{Y}n barchus-{w}ych</l>
      <l>{Y}n {w}edhus-{w}ych {y}n Nudh oesog.</l>
   </lg>
   <p>G{w}il. Midlton.</p>
</div>
